CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 16, 1962, pg. 6 reads: "Masons' Conference - Masons of the Prince Hall Affiliation held their annual mid-year conference at the Penn-Sheraton Hotel, Pittsburgh, on June 2. Left to right: John H. King, D.D.G.M.; James C. Jones, D.D.G.L.; Henry M. Baysmore Jr., M.W.G.M.; Henry Bailey, D.D.G.M.; the Rev. Clarence A. Burrell, D.D., and James Thompson, D.D.G.L.  The annual session of the Prince Hall Masons will be held at Philadelphia in December. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Masons of the Prince Hall Affiliation, from left: John H. King, James C. Jones, Henry M. Baysmore Jr., Henry Bailey, Rev. Clarence A. Burrell, and James Thompson, standing in Penn Sheraton Hotel for annual mid-year conference
